  ('findlay','Dietsch Brothers Ice Cream Social','Food','🍦','2026-06-22T15:00:00-04:00','2026-06-22T18:00:00-04:00','Dietsch Brothers Fine Chocolates & Ice Cream','400 W Main Cross St, Findlay, OH','Pay per item','Dietsch Brothers',false,'A Findlay tradition since 1937. Stop in for hand-dipped ice cream and homemade chocolates on a summer afternoon.','approved'),
  ('findlay','Flag City Balloon Fest Planning Walk','Community','🎈','2026-06-24T18:00:00-04:00','2026-06-24T19:30:00-04:00','Emory Adams Park','1212 Lima Ave, Findlay, OH','Free','Flag City Balloon Fest Committee',false,'Volunteers and curious neighbors welcome. Learn how the annual hot air balloon festival comes together and how you can help.','approved'),
