  ('findlay','Beginner Smartphone Help Session','Education','📱','2026-06-23T13:00:00-04:00','2026-06-23T14:30:00-04:00','Findlay-Hancock County Public Library','206 Broadway St, Findlay, OH','Free','Library Tech Help Desk',false,'Friendly one-on-one help with your phone or tablet. Learn texting, photos, video calls, and apps at your own pace. No question is too small.','approved'),
  ('findlay','Sunrise Yoga in the Park','Sports','🧘','2026-06-21T07:30:00-04:00','2026-06-21T08:30:00-04:00','Riverside Park','231 McManness Ave, Findlay, OH','$5 suggested','Findlay Community Yoga',false,'Gentle, all-levels outdoor yoga to start your weekend. Bring your own mat. Modifications offered for every pose.','approved'),
