  ('findlay','Food Truck Friday','Food','🌮','2026-06-26T11:00:00-04:00','2026-06-26T14:00:00-04:00','Dorney Plaza / City Building','318 Dorney Plaza, Findlay, OH','Pay per item','Downtown Findlay Inc.',false,'A rotating lineup of local food trucks serving lunch downtown. A great midday break with plenty of seating.','approved'),
